---
// VoicesSection.astro
---

<section 
  class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-ink)] to-[var(--color-ink-2)]"
>
  <div class="max-w-[1140px] mx-auto px-7">
    
    <div class="text-center max-w-[640px] mx-auto mb-14">
      <span class="block font-sans font-semibold text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[var(--color-amber)] mb-5">
        Voices from the Circle
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-serif font-light text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,2.9rem)] tracking-tight leading-[1.08] text-[var(--color-cream)] my-[0.4em]">
        What people are <em class="italic text-[var(--color-rose)]">saying</em>.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-cream)]/60 text-[1.06rem] leading-relaxed">
        Anonymous, overheard — the way trust usually travels.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-5 max-md:grid-cols-1">
      
      <div class="bg-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.04] border border-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.10] rounded-[22px] p-8">
        <span class="block font-sans font-semibold text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.45] mb-4">
          I heard someone say
        </span>
        <p class="font-serif italic text-[1.15rem] leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.92]">
          "I stopped trying to heal alone the day I found a circle that wouldn't let me."
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.04] border border-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.10] rounded-[22px] p-8">
        <span class="block font-sans font-semibold text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.45] mb-4">
          I heard someone say
        </span>
        <p class="font-serif italic text-[1.15rem] leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.92]">
          "As a therapist, I finally feel held by the same thing I offer everyone else."
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.04] border border-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.10] rounded-[22px] p-8">
        <span class="block font-sans font-semibold text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.45] mb-4">
          I heard someone say
        </span>
        <p class="font-serif italic text-[1.15rem] leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.92]">
          "It's the first wellness space that didn't feel like a transaction. It felt like belonging."
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.04] border border-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.10] rounded-[22px] p-8">
        <span class="block font-sans font-semibold text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.45] mb-4">
          I heard someone say
        </span>
        <p class="font-serif italic text-[1.15rem] leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-cream)]/[0.92]">
          "We built the structure together — and somehow that's exactly what made it feel safe."
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>